Module wargames

Class WarGamesModel

java.lang.Object
edu.ntnu.idatt2001.runarin.frontend.model.WarGamesModel
public class WarGamesModel extends Object
MVC Model-class for holding values used in the GUI. This class holds all static data which does not need a listener, and that can be accessed when called for.
